rows.label: qst106021_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome back, mo. Have you
gathered the materials for
the new outfit, mo?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0002
rows.name: Yes, we've gathered everything we need.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0003
rows.name:
Nee-sama, please make the
best outfit with this, mo!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0004
rows.name:
Leave it to me, mo. I will
make an outfit that meets
all of Hana's hopes, mo.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0005
rows.name:
Well then, Kiku will move to another
room to make the clothes, mo.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, Masterpon mentioned that he had
something to discuss with you, mo.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0007
rows.name:
...Don't tell me my adult body
is already complete, mo?!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0008
rows.name:
Isn't that a bit too soon to
be thinking that, Hana-chan?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0009
rows.name:
Even Masterpon can't finish
it that quickly, mo.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0010
rows.name:
He said that Hana also needs
to make preparations before
the modification, mo.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0011
rows.name:
Preparations, mo? Should I do some
exercises to loosen up my body, mo?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0012
rows.name:
In that case, there's
no need to worry, mo.

rows.label: qst106021_msg0013
rows.name:
As you can see, Hana can
bend all her joints freely
in any direction, mo!

rows.label: qst106021_msg0014
rows.name:
It's one of Hana's
specialties, mo! Should
Hana demonstrate it here, mo?

rows.label: qst106021_msg0015
rows.name:
No, that won't be necessary,
mo. Just don't forget to
talk to Masterpon, mo.
